This paper proposes a streaming subspace estimation algorithm for detecting low-dimensional linear structure from incomplete data efficiently. The paper focuses on computational complexity and storage, which are key concerns in machine learning and data science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
